Class AbstractObservableLocalAutonomousReader

    public abstract class AbstractObservableLocalAutonomousReader
extends AbstractObservableLocalReader
    Extends AbstractObservableLocalReader to allow the reader implementation to call back the core when card insertion and removal events occur.

    1.0
